Package: isochrones
Type: Package
Title: Utilities for Isochrone Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(person(given = "Tyler", family = "Muffly", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "tyler.muffly@dhha.org"))
Description: Utility scripts and helpers for analyzing drive-time isochrones and
    healthcare accessibility. Functions cover dataset retrieval, geocoding,
    polygon creation, and summary reporting.
